{
  "chapter": 28,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十八回「火窟」。王风与血奴被困于李大娘庄院地下的石牢之中，石牢内有两具骷髅，其中一具头戴紫金白玉冠。血奴认出那是魔王的遗骸，悲愤交加，欲与李大娘拼命却被量天尺克制。李大娘透露魔王与鹦鹉已在十日内自裁殉主，她则继续贩卖珠宝以维持约定。王风与李大娘唇枪舌剑，讨论蚯蚓蜈蚣等求生之物，李大娘启动石牢中的黑油机关，四壁燃起火蛇，欲将二人活活烧死。危急时刻，传说中每七年降临人间一次的血鹦鹉忽然现身，王风兑现愿望，血鹦鹉垂下绳索，王风抱起昏迷的血奴飞出火窟。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你又在卖弄什么阴谋诡计？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你莫非不肯相信所看见的事实？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "我其实也不是一个怎样贪心的人，那些珠宝有一半到手我其实已经很满足，随时都准备放人了，谁知道，他们在下面不过十日，魔王便不甘屈辱尽断经脉自裁，鹦鹉亦相继殉主自尽。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "以他们的身份我也知这个石牢实在太过委屈，本来准备将这个石牢加以布置的了，可是地面都还未弄好，事情就已经发生。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "这件事如果传了出去，我们之间的约定固然终结，我更绝不会活到现在，你们知道了魔王血鹦鹉已经不在人间，又岂会不立即取我性命？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我们将珠宝完全找回来之后你就要将人交出，到时候你如何向我们交代？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你们永远都不能将那些珠宝完全找到的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "这句话是什么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你们那边将珠宝找回来，我这边便又将一些珠宝卖出去，虽然你们找回来的那些珠宝不能再出手，那不过其中小小的一部分，那许多珠宝，何时才卖尽？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_nu",
      "speaker_name": "血奴",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你就是这样卑鄙。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_xue_nu",
      "text": "你还有什么兵器暗器？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你是否也想试试能否跳上来对付我？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我还有自知之明。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你是不是不要命，随时都在准备拼命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你不肯自己跳几下给我看，我只好自己想个办法要你大跳了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你准备怎样？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这陷阱的上面本来有一块几百斤的铁板，将铁板放下就算轻功很好，亦只有在下面等死的份儿，只要我断绝供应清水食物，不出三日你们在下面就不渴死也得饿死，据我所知饿也可以饿的人发疯，到时只要我将铁板再打开，不难见到你在下面猴子般乱跳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "三两天还饿不死我这个人，这石牢里面说不定还有可吃的东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "泥土里的蚯蚓还是缝中的蜈蚣？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "蚯蚓、蜈蚣据我所知都是非常可口的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你吃过那些东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "还没有这样的机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "这一次是你的机会了，只不知，你是不是真的敢吃那些东西？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "连命我都敢拼，还有什么事情不敢。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "连那些东西你都吃，我就想不佩服你都不成了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "只不知血奴是不是也吃得下那些东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "她就算不吃也不要紧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "一天半天没有东西入口，我相信她还支持得住。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我听不懂你这句话。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你以为你真的能够将我囚在这个石牢活活饿死？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "难道你有本领，逃出这个石牢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "一天半实在已太多，也许两三个时辰之后我就在石牢外面，那会子最好你已远离这里，不给我遇上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "不成你真的有穿墙入壁，飞天遁地的本领？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我不是妖魔鬼怪，也不是法师。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你那是什么本领？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "也不是什么本领，只不过我身上带着一支削铁如泥的宝剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "原来你就只是还有一支削铁如泥的宝剑。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你好像并不担心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我担心什么？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "这石牢的石头，封口的铁板，莫非连削铁如泥的宝剑都削不入？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "那只是普通的石，普通的铁。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "你难道不怕我走出来找你算账。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "怎会不怕！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "我看，你简直就不是害怕的样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "如果你现在能够出来找我算账，我就真的害怕了，可惜你最少也要两三个时辰之后才能够出外。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我根本就没有打算将你们囚在石牢里头活活饿死，因为那最少要两三天时间。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我没有那么好的耐性，就连三个时辰的耐性我也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我现在就要你活虾般乱跳。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_li_da_niang",
      "text": "这石牢下面莫非还有什么机关？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "当然有，而且已发动。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你那支削铁如泥的宝剑能不能将这些火蛇削断？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_da_niang",
      "speaker_name": "李大娘",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "半个时辰之后，你如果还不变做一只活虾的话，那我就真的服了你。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "王风！王风！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "你真的是那只血鹦鹉？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "本来就是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "为什么你竟会在这个时候，这个地方出现？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "因为你在这个时候有难，在这个地方遇难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "听你这样说，你似乎真的一只通灵的魔鸟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "听你的口气，你却好像并不高兴见到我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "谁说不高兴，我高兴得简直要跳起五丈。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "就只是五丈？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "只要我能够跳高五丈，我已经可以离开这个要命的石牢，火窟！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你想离开？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "不想的是疯子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我知道你绝不是疯子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "如果是疯子我就绝不会还记得你欠我两个愿望这件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你现在，就想要那两个愿望？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "想极了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你的第一个愿望是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "现在我反而怀疑你到底是一只灵鸟还是一只呆鸟了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "你的第一个愿望莫非就是赶陕离开这个要命的地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_feng",
      "speaker_name": "王风",
      "listener": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "text": "越快就越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xue_ying_wu",
      "speaker_name": "血鹦鹉",
      "listener": "char_wang_feng",
      "text": "我这就让你得到一个愿望。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 474,
